title: Faker Top 5 Pentakills 2015

embed.description: In th is video I showcase Faker's top 5 pentakills (in my opinion) of 2015, or season 5. body: Hey all, I recently created a youtube channel and have started working on montages and top 5's, for my first video, I've created a 'Faker Top 5 Pentakills of 2015'.
